"A.P.241/9/29": "HA! I've caught you now, Commander!"

"Huh!?
I thought I attacked your blind spot...! Wait, are you not...?"
"Commander Huey...?"
"Ah I'm sorry! Sorry! I don't know how I confused you for him, I'm the lowest of the low!"
"I'm so sorry, I trusted my gut instinct on a strong feeling..."
"What's wrong Stratos, exhausted already?"

"Oh, <%me>!
What a coincidence meeting you here!"

"<%me>...?
The Guardian!?"
"Aiiiiieeeeee....! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry! I did an offensive thing!"
"Hahaha, so that's it. <%me>, sorry to drag you into this."
"Because her actions reflect on myself, could you forgive me? Save for my honor!"
"1. What's with her?"
"2．What were you doing?"
"Oh that's right, an introduction."
"It's better if I we explain it from this introduction."
"Combat Division, New Tactics Development Group. The name's Stratos!"
"Stratos is a third generation like you. She has already completed the fundamentals of each class, I hope."
"I'm extremely grateful!"
"By the way, New Tactics Development Group is where we experiement with new classes and new ideas."
"New ideas are needed for this type of thing! And thus we selected Stratos and put her in charge of it!"
"I'm extremely grateful!"
"However, this is difficult... While we were researching on a way to fight multiple enemies at once within a single fighting force, we couldn't get permission..."
"While myself and Claris Claes providing support, we have already established our fighting styles. So we're not very flexible in this regard."
"I'm extremely grateful..."

"There, <%me>!
If you don't mind, but could you be an adviser for Stratos?"
"Eeehhh! Commander, that's generous of you!"
"Well, the ARKS with the most freedom is <%me>. Mingling with <%me>, will provide a source of encouragement!"
"And of course, the best person to master the new class would be <%me>."

"<%me>.
Would you please cooperate with the following ARKS?"
"1．Leave it to me"
"2．Don't expect too much"
"I'm extremely grateful...!"
"Heh, you sure are humble! But it's ok, you're fine! I know it!"

"<%me>!
Thank you in advance!"
"If you don't mind, could you tell me about your combat histories and stories?! By all means!"
